question:
What is the output of the following code?

```java
class Test {
    int x;
    Test(int x) { this.x = x; }
    void modify(Test t) { t.x = t.x + 10; }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Test obj = new Test(10);
        obj.modify(obj);
        System.out.println(obj.x);
    }
}
```
